title: About Rank
body: I've gotten plat about a month ago and ive been maintaining it ever since but now season has ended and i saw my friends got their borders and rewards i was wondering why havent i recieved mine? anyone know ? is it because im honor 2?{{sticker:cass-cry}}

replies.body: NO worries just yet fam, those ranked rewards will still be going out over the month. If you don't see your rewards in about a week or two go ahead and hit us up in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
